WEBVTT

00:08:29.401 --> 00:08:33.798
And days have turned into months,
months into years.

00:08:34.483 --> 00:08:38.055
A refugee's stay is supposed
to be temporary.

00:08:38.079 --> 00:08:41.400
Back to Doaa and Bassem in the water.

00:08:41.424 --> 00:08:45.773
It was their second day,
and Bassem was getting very weak.

00:08:46.764 --> 00:08:50.765
And now it was Doaa's turn
to say to Bassem,

00:08:50.789 --> 00:08:56.472
"My love, please hold on to hope,
to our future. We will make it."

00:08:57.376 --> 00:09:00.057
And he said to her,